---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 166
By: Ruysbroeck
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Volition, Obedience and Conformity=Volition
  - 914
---
The measure of your holiness is proportionate to the goodness of your
will. Consider then how good your will is, and the degree of your
holiness will be clear to you. For every one is as holy, as he is good
of heart.
